      { "number": 104, "question_text": "The secretary told me that Mr. Rich had gone out. The secretary told me, \"______\"", "options": { "A": "Mr. Rich was going out", "B": "Mr. Rich goes out", "C": "Mr. Rich has gone out", "D": "Mr. Rich is going out" }, "correct_answer": "C" },
